Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.14,0:00:23.27,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}katahou no mimitabu de kiku sotsugyou no canon
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.27,0:00:29.23,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}hitori demo daijoubu yo tte mekureteru watashi no story
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.23,0:00:31.51,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}dareka no sei ni shitai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.51,0:00:35.70,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}tsurai naa iya iya
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.70,0:00:41.05,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}kanashikutte naite bakkari itara me ga tokete nakunatta
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.67,0:00:46.47,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}aki ni nari mata fuyu ni nari hitotsu toshi wo totta
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.10,0:00:53.26,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}tooku made nigete iru tsumori demo owaranai kimi no story
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.26,0:00:55.52,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}niya niya waratte iru
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.52,0:00:59.11,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}fugainaiya iya
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.11,0:01:05.25,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}sugari nagara oikakete mitemo ashige ni saretemo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:07.44,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}aita ana wo fusagou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.44,0:01:10.36,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}chigai nai ya iya
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.36,0:01:17.74,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}fugainai ya iya
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.33,0:01:28.36,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}tsurai naa iya iya
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.18,0:00:06.24,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}My hometown lay buried in snow the morning I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.07,0:00:11.78,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}I looked up at the blue sky with my tiny hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.09,0:00:18.41,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}The face of the girl next door that I've known so well...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.14,0:00:23.27,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's as familiar as the graduation canon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.27,0:00:29.23,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Thriving in solitude has been mistaken as my life story.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.23,0:00:31.51,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}I want to blame it on someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.51,0:00:35.70,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's so difficult. No, I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.70,0:00:41.05,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Tears and sorrow caused me to miss my chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.67,0:00:46.47,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Autumn passed, winter came again, and I became a year older.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.10,0:00:53.26,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}You think you've run far away, but your story never ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.26,0:00:55.52,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}And yet, you're smirking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.52,0:00:59.11,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's so cowardly. I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.11,0:01:05.25,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Even if I have to cling to you, chase after you, and get kicked down...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:07.44,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}...I'll close the hole that's opened...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.44,0:01:10.36,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}...without a doubt. No...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.36,0:01:17.74,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's so cowardly. No...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.33,0:01:28.36,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's so difficult. I hate it. I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.96,0:01:39.55,clover,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon, Dr. Satsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.96,0:01:39.55,sign,,0,0,0,,Rehab Room
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.98,0:01:42.69,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're Hagumi-chan's...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.69,0:01:44.39,clover,,0,0,0,,Yamada-san, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.23,0:01:46.07,clover,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.07,0:01:48.14,clover,,0,0,0,,I brought some food for her...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.68,0:01:50.81,clover,,0,0,0,,...but she wasn't in her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.29,0:01:55.51,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, about that. She just finished up her rehab...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.51,0:01:58.38,clover,,0,0,0,,...so she went to the contrast bath with her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.24,0:02:01.36,clover,,0,0,0,,No! That person isn't her father!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.24,0:02:01.36,note,,0,0,0,,"Contrast bath" is a medical term where you alternately dip your limb in warm and cold water to keep the swelling down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.04,0:02:09.11,clover,,0,0,0,,Doctor, um... about Hagu-chan's condition...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.52,0:02:12.85,clover,,0,0,0,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.85,0:02:16.03,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm sick of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.03,0:02:18.26,clover,,0,0,0,,Ryo, please bear with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.26,0:02:20.78,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm sick of doing this every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.78,0:02:23.22,clover,,0,0,0,,I wanna play soccer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.62,0:02:23.66,clover,,0,0,0,,That boy was in a car accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.70,0:02:26.95,clover,,0,0,0,,He's been in rehab here since last month.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.76,0:02:29.83,clover,,0,0,0,,It's difficult for young children.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.55,0:02:34.26,clover,,0,0,0,,Rehab is also a battle against pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.90,0:02:39.46,clover,,0,0,0,,Even a grown man would be in pain and afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.94,0:02:44.70,clover,,0,0,0,,People will often give up once they've healed to a certain degree.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.52,0:02:51.04,clover,,0,0,0,,But Hagumi-san must regain something more than routine movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.98,0:02:56.46,clover,,0,0,0,,Whether she can return to being an artist hinges on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:02:59.66,clover,,0,0,0,,On top of that, her injury is on her dominant hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.52,0:03:02.67,clover,,0,0,0,,But she's strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:05.01,clover,,0,0,0,,She's not afraid of pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.43,0:03:09.35,clover,,0,0,0,,No, I'm sure she must be afraid, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:15.42,clover,,0,0,0,,...her fear of not being able to draw must be overwhelmingly more powerful than her fear of pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:17.53,clover,,0,0,0,,Hagu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.53,0:03:19.01,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.54,0:03:23.61,clover,,0,0,0,,Ah, you came again, Yamada-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.57,0:03:27.31,clover,,0,0,0,,Have you been taking care of yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.66,0:03:31.18,clover,,0,0,0,,I have! I'm all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.18,0:03:34.36,clover,,0,0,0,,I've been going all-out and giving everything my best, just like you, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:37.30,clover,,0,0,0,,And I've got a lot of confidence in today's menu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.89,0:03:38.88,clover,,0,0,0,,What is it, Ayu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.00,0:03:40.15,clover,,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.00,0:03:53.93,sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\be1\fs40\bord2\c&H3A45B1&\3c&H14171C&\pos(515,293)}odor
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:42.46,clover,,0,0,0,,It's sweet-boiled beef tendons and kumquat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.08,0:03:46.07,clover,,0,0,0,,Now this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.07,0:03:53.93,clover,,0,0,0,,The hearty scent of beef fat is mixing with the fruity scent of the kumquat and... man, I don't even know what to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.59,0:03:58.45,clover,,0,0,0,,I thought she might be needing some collagen...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.45,0:04:02.30,clover,,0,0,0,,...and I added some kumquat for the vitamin C!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.30,0:04:05.74,clover,,0,0,0,,This should, like, also keep her from catching a cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.35,0:04:09.59,clover,,0,0,0,,It's tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.59,0:04:10.41,clover,,0,0,0,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.72,0:04:11.94,clover,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.94,0:04:14.41,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, please have some also if you'd like, Dr. Satsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.41,0:04:16.60,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, my, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.60,0:04:17.87,clover,,0,0,0,,Dr. Satsuki, hold on a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.65,0:04:24.09,clover,,0,0,0,,See? Delicious, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.92,0:04:26.83,clover,,0,0,0,,Y-Yamada-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.83,0:04:29.32,clover,,0,0,0,,I'd like to make a comment from a medical perspective...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.32,0:04:30.30,clover,,0,0,0,,Dr. Satsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.30,0:04:35.99,clover,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Nutrition is important, but there's absolutely no need for you to put everything into one dish...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.13,0:04:37.31,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're the boy from earlier. Would you like some as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.99,0:04:42.32,clover,,0,0,0,,{\an8}This is why traditional Japanese cuisine involves one soup dish and three vegetable dishes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.33,0:04:38.36,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:40.62,clover,,0,0,0,,Would you like some too, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.70,0:04:42.32,clover,,0,0,0,,My, is it all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:48.23,clover,,0,0,0,,Crap! Even more victims!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.23,0:04:51.21,clover,,0,0,0,,Someone call an ambulance... Oh, this is the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.21,0:04:53.77,clover,,0,0,0,,Delish! This is so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.77,0:04:55.46,clover,,0,0,0,,Gosh, it's already gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.46,0:04:57.55,clover,,0,0,0,,My cooking is totally popular!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.55,0:04:59.04,clover,,0,0,0,,I'll make more and bring it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.04,0:05:00.09,clover,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.09,0:05:01.06,clover,,0,0,0,,Yamada genocide!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.06,0:05:02.39,clover,,0,0,0,,No{\fscx200}-{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.84,0:05:07.61,clover,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.03,0:05:16.90,clover,,0,0,0,,Okay then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:20.17,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I made everyone happy today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.17,0:05:23.56,thoughts,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, wait a second! Where on earth did you get an idea like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.19,0:05:29.15,clover,,0,0,0,,It turned into a bit of a commotion, but that must mean they're looking forward to the next time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:38.25,sign,,0,0,0,,Morita
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.96,0:05:45.38,clover,,0,0,0,,Where in the world did you go...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.62,0:05:50.58,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I'll leave a video phone behind when I'm going away again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.84,0:05:53.64,sign,,0,0,0,,Morita
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:53.31,clover,,0,0,0,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.33,0:06:10.53,clover,,0,0,0,,Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.53,0:06:12.20,clover,,0,0,0,,Rika!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.20,0:06:14.16,clover,,0,0,0,,Rika, Rika!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.94,0:06:16.45,clover,,0,0,0,,Why do you keep coming day after after day?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.16,0:06:15.69,clover,,0,0,0,,Olé!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.58,0:06:19.53,clover,,0,0,0,,We don't have any appointments with you today!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.70,0:06:19.53,clover,,0,0,0,,Rika, Rika!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.53,0:06:22.18,clover,,0,0,0,,And actually, we'll hold all of our meetings elsewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.16,0:06:23.71,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, my goodness, move! Move, punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.18,0:06:24.18,clover,,0,0,0,,so don't ever come here again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.71,0:06:25.32,clover,,0,0,0,,Ow! Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:26.43,clover,,0,0,0,,Rika!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.91,0:06:30.34,clover,,0,0,0,,Rika!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.34,0:06:33.47,clover,,0,0,0,,Damn that suspicious head.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.47,0:06:35.60,clover,,0,0,0,,I'll finally expose him tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.60,0:06:37.94,clover,,0,0,0,,That's right, I'm gonna make it clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.94,0:06:40.61,clover,,0,0,0,,Both the issue with Rika-san and the secret behind his hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:47.82,clover,,0,0,0,,Yamada?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.46,0:06:53.65,clover,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:00.62,clover,,0,0,0,,Here, Takemoto-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.39,0:07:02.62,clover,,0,0,0,,Are these okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.67,0:07:07.14,clover,,0,0,0,,It might be pretty to paste some shattered white pottery onto my tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.77,0:07:10.18,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm happy you can use them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.18,0:07:11.63,clover,,0,0,0,,Parts always break off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.96,0:07:16.19,clover,,0,0,0,,M-Morita-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.19,0:07:17.35,clover,,0,0,0,,Where's Mouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.78,0:07:18.60,clover,,0,0,0,,But why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.60,0:07:20.60,clover,,0,0,0,,We've been looking for you! Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.92,0:07:22.79,clover,,0,0,0,,Where were you all this time...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.79,0:07:23.81,clover,,0,0,0,,I heard from Mayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.81,0:07:24.98,clover,,0,0,0,,Where's Mouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.98,0:07:28.16,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh... W-West Eifuku Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.16,0:07:30.19,clover,,0,0,0,,That big one by the park...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.53,0:07:31.25,clover,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.25,0:07:32.25,clover,,0,0,0,,Morita-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.25,0:07:34.69,clover,,0,0,0,,Wait! Hey, wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.27,0:07:36.98,clover,,0,0,0,,Morita-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.62,0:07:40.91,clover,,0,0,0,,M-Morita? He's back?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.91,0:07:43.40,clover,,0,0,0,,Did someone say Morita's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.40,0:07:45.04,clover,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you just say Morita?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:48.51,clover,,0,0,0,,He put the Robot Club's action figures on a net auction without asking us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.51,0:07:49.81,clover,,0,0,0,,Where is that man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.81,0:07:53.05,clover,,0,0,0,,That man is the reincarnation of Taikan-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.81,0:07:53.05,note,,0,0,0,,Yokoyama Taikan (1868-1958) was an important leader in the Japanese traditional school of modern Japanese art.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.60,0:07:55.44,clover,,0,0,0,,Well... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.28,0:07:58.18,clover,,0,0,0,,Why, all of a sudden...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.71,0:08:01.54,clover,,0,0,0,,No one could figure out where he was all of this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.58,0:08:05.10,clover,,0,0,0,,On top of that, how did he know about Hagu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:07.65,clover,,0,0,0,,I asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.85,0:08:13.23,clover,,0,0,0,,I asked Mayama in an e-mail to find Morita-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.13,0:08:19.44,clover,,0,0,0,,Since Mayama is in Spain, I didn't know if it was a good idea to tell him about Hagu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.76,0:08:21.13,clover,,0,0,0,,But, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.58,0:08:25.50,clover,,0,0,0,,Takemoto-kun... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.95,0:08:26.79,clover,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.17,0:08:30.47,clover,,0,0,0,,Yamada-san, there's no need to apologize to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.08,0:08:33.27,clover,,0,0,0,,Please, spare me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.15,0:08:36.95,clover,,0,0,0,,Um, well then, I'll be going, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:40.35,clover,,0,0,0,,Morita-san didn't seem like himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.35,0:08:42.16,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm worried about what he might do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.52,0:08:51.30,clover,,0,0,0,,T-Takemoto-kun! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.27,0:08:55.34,clover,,0,0,0,,T-Takemoto-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.04,0:08:58.21,clover,,0,0,0,,A-Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.21,0:09:00.07,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:03.72,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:08.75,clover,,0,0,0,,Yamada-san, please lend me your bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.77,0:09:11.59,clover,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.15,0:09:16.75,clover,,0,0,0,,Even if I'm 100% sure to be rejected...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.75,0:09:18.17,clover,,0,0,0,,Even if I look pathetic...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.00,0:09:21.46,clover,,0,0,0,,Even if I can't even afford a single bouquet...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.25,0:09:24.16,clover,,0,0,0,,Right now, she's the one in pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.60,0:09:26.31,clover,,0,0,0,,She's the one who's suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.52,0:09:34.86,clover,,0,0,0,,This isn't the time for me to call myself powerless and swallow in self-pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.09,0:09:37.03,clover,,0,0,0,,I won't make a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.56,0:09:38.99,clover,,0,0,0,,I don't want to make a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.17,0:09:42.55,clover,,0,0,0,,I want to be at least that much of a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.69,0:10:16.90,clover,,0,0,0,,All right, I'm gonna push down slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.37,0:10:20.15,clover,,0,0,0,,One, two, three.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.54,0:10:25.59,clover,,0,0,0,,Does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.04,0:10:27.33,clover,,0,0,0,,Don't push yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.23,0:10:29.39,clover,,0,0,0,,It hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.47,0:10:31.12,clover,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.77,0:10:35.25,clover,,0,0,0,,I can still take this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.21,0:10:38.52,clover,,0,0,0,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.52,0:10:39.47,clover,,0,0,0,,I hate this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.47,0:10:41.80,clover,,0,0,0,,I don't want any more anesthesia or rehab!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.71,0:10:44.19,clover,,0,0,0,,It's the boy from yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.19,0:10:45.65,clover,,0,0,0,,I've had enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.65,0:10:47.30,clover,,0,0,0,,It's not gonna get better anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.84,0:10:49.77,clover,,0,0,0,,It's never gonna move again, is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.77,0:10:51.77,clover,,0,0,0,,Then I don't wanna hurt anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.77,0:10:53.70,clover,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.65,0:10:59.50,clover,,0,0,0,,Hagu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.17,0:11:03.91,clover,,0,0,0,,Why don't we go outside for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.41,0:11:17.42,clover,,0,0,0,,It must be nice to be able to throw a tantrum like that kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.15,0:11:20.41,clover,,0,0,0,,Feel free to throw a tantrum as well, Hagu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.71,0:11:26.55,clover,,0,0,0,,You're in this for the long haul. If you keep your emotions pent up, you won't last.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.51,0:11:33.82,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid... that if I start, I won't be able to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.60,0:11:36.82,clover,,0,0,0,,It's all right. Say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.80,0:11:40.72,clover,,0,0,0,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.82,0:11:46.64,clover,,0,0,0,,I've been causing you so much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.98,0:11:50.29,clover,,0,0,0,,At this rate, you're going to hate me someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:52.45,clover,,0,0,0,,I won't hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.82,0:11:53.95,clover,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.41,0:12:03.02,clover,,0,0,0,,You know, I even took care of you when you used to wet your bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.02,0:12:07.05,clover,,0,0,0,,If I thought you were too much trouble, I would've hated you already.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.05,0:12:09.30,clover,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about, seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.87,0:12:12.47,clover,,0,0,0,,When I gave you a ride in my car, you got carsick and threw up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.88,0:12:15.30,clover,,0,0,0,,When I took you to the river, you got carried away by the current.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.68,0:12:19.64,clover,,0,0,0,,No matter what else happens, I'm not going to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.17,0:12:23.44,clover,,0,0,0,,I won't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.58,0:12:30.94,clover,,0,0,0,,Shuu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.72,0:12:38.25,clover,,0,0,0,,Shuu-chan...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.21,0:12:44.92,clover,,0,0,0,,The truth is... I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.70,0:12:50.30,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm so scared I don't know what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.56,0:12:56.48,clover,,0,0,0,,What if I don't get better? What if I can't draw again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.05,0:13:00.09,clover,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shuu-chan, what does living mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.09,0:13:04.33,clover,,0,0,0,,You breathe and you eat. What else are you supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.33,0:13:05.02,clover,,0,0,0,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.73,0:13:06.99,clover,,0,0,0,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:20.18,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}kimi no matsuge de yureteru suishou no tsubu\NA drop of liquid dances on your eyelashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.52,0:13:11.25,clover,,0,0,0,,Not drawing anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.29,0:13:14.92,clover,,0,0,0,,How could I live...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.74,0:13:19.67,clover,,0,0,0,,For the rest of my life... for such a long time...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.62,0:13:30.05,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}hontou wa hitori-bocchi\NYou're actually all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.63,0:13:21.80,clover,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.37,0:13:23.84,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm so scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.44,0:13:42.58,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}kabe ni kaita midori-iro no door wo akete\NThe vast ocean of time expands...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.94,0:13:35.67,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Once, when I was little, I saw God.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,0:13:39.93,thoughts,,0,0,0,,If...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.98,0:13:52.03,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}hirogaru toki no umi\N...beyond the open, green door drawn on the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.02,0:13:49.96,thoughts,,0,0,0,,If I didn't have this paper and pencil, what would I have done?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.70,0:14:01.83,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}dakedo kimi wa mou kizuki hajimeru darou\NBut you'll begin to notice...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.45,0:14:04.95,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Being alone among all these people... how would I have lived...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.52,0:14:11.45,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}kawari yuku keshiki ni\N...that your world isn't the same anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.45,0:14:20.94,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}tsuki no light ga namida de tobichiru yoru ni\N...on the night when the moonlight reflects off your tears...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.04,0:14:15.10,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.79,0:14:22.04,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I was okay because I had my pencil and paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.94,0:14:28.57,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}{\an9}namida de tobichiru yoru ni\NWhen it reflects off of your tears...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.94,0:14:31.53,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Drawing gave me life and protected me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.57,0:14:38.01,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}erabarete kimi wa megami ni naru\NYou were chosen to become a goddess...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.09,0:14:39.33,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Ah, God...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.86,0:14:47.74,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}dare ni mo satorarezu\N...but nobody noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.46,0:14:50.11,thoughts,,0,0,0,,If I were ever to stop drawing, at that moment I will return my life to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.31,0:14:57.76,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}soshite kimi wa sugu aruki hajimeru darou\NAnd with your freed soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.24,0:15:07.22,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}hanatareta tamashii de\N...you'll begin to walk away immediately...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.22,0:15:17.16,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}tsuki no light ga namida de tobichiru yoru ni\N...on the night when the moonlight reflects off your tears...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.93,0:15:10.30,clover,,0,0,0,,Hagu, let's go back to the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.68,0:15:13.04,clover,,0,0,0,,You don't want to yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.22,0:15:16.41,clover,,0,0,0,,Then let's drink something warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.05,0:15:18.19,clover,,0,0,0,,How about some cocoa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.16,0:15:21.97,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}{\an9}namida de tobichiru yoru ni\NWhen it reflects off of your tears...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.74,0:15:19.78,clover,,0,0,0,,Hold on for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.97,0:15:31.54,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}namida de tobichiru yoru ni\NWhen it reflects off of your tears...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.82,0:15:32.09,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I'm certain that I made a vow back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.20,0:15:36.34,thoughts,,0,0,0,,...with my invisible God.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.11,0:15:44.92,thoughts,,0,0,0,,That's why I've been struggling so hard to keep that one promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.43,0:15:48.62,thoughts,,0,0,0,,God...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.11,0:15:54.39,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Right now, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.75,0:16:02.74,clover,,0,0,0,,Hagu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.66,0:16:04.62,clover,,0,0,0,,Hagu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.62,0:16:05.55,clover,,0,0,0,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.00,0:16:07.58,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, Takemoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.58,0:16:08.58,clover,,0,0,0,,Where's Hagu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.58,0:16:11.23,clover,,0,0,0,,Well, she's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.23,0:16:12.88,clover,,0,0,0,,She was here just a second ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.19,0:16:15.34,clover,,0,0,0,,It's Morita-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.79,0:16:16.76,clover,,0,0,0,,Morita?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.25,0:16:18.53,clover,,0,0,0,,He's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.99,0:16:24.15,clover,,0,0,0,,Morita-san learned about Hagu-chan's injury and said that he was going to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.28,0:16:26.31,clover,,0,0,0,,Morita did?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.95,0:16:40.24,clover,,0,0,0,,This place is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.49,0:16:45.00,clover,,0,0,0,,We used to call it our "secret base".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.89,0:16:46.91,clover,,0,0,0,,My older brother and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.08,0:16:49.41,clover,,0,0,0,,Your older brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.11,0:16:54.25,clover,,0,0,0,,Did you lose weight?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.97,0:16:55.99,clover,,0,0,0,,Same to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.77,0:16:58.05,clover,,0,0,0,,I was surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.05,0:16:59.15,clover,,0,0,0,,It was so sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.80,0:17:02.27,clover,,0,0,0,,Did you get to go to a lot of places again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.80,0:17:05.06,clover,,0,0,0,,Did you get to see a lot of things again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.37,0:17:07.36,clover,,0,0,0,,Did you make a lot of things?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.69,0:17:09.11,clover,,0,0,0,,Were you able to do a lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.96,0:17:13.37,clover,,0,0,0,,P-Please wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.67,0:17:15.29,clover,,0,0,0,,I'll make it get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.62,0:17:17.07,clover,,0,0,0,,Then we can again...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.96,0:17:20.95,clover,,0,0,0,,I'll draw a lot again...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.66,0:17:26.87,clover,,0,0,0,,Then we can show them to each other again...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.34,0:17:31.35,clover,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.68,0:17:35.83,clover,,0,0,0,,Stop drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.87,0:17:38.01,clover,,0,0,0,,You don't need to draw anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.62,0:17:48.10,clover,,0,0,0,,It's absurd to think that your life won't have a meaning unless you leave some work behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.48,0:17:51.05,clover,,0,0,0,,Just living is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:53.45,clover,,0,0,0,,Just being together is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.52,0:17:57.00,clover,,0,0,0,,That's all I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.93,0:18:05.26,clover,,0,0,0,,Unsurpassed words of kindness flowed out of his mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.54,0:18:10.79,clover,,0,0,0,,His voice was so gentle... so kind and full of sorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.72,0:18:16.75,clover,,0,0,0,,It was as if he were calling to me from somewhere far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.50,0:18:21.80,clover,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:25.25,clover,,0,0,0,,I mean, I'd never heard it before...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.49,0:18:28.16,clover,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.51,0:18:31.92,clover,,0,0,0,,I'd never heard him sound like this before...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.23,0:18:35.42,clover,,0,0,0,,Please tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.34,0:18:45.40,clover,,0,0,0,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.98,0:18:47.03,clover,,0,0,0,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.98,0:18:51.50,clover,,0,0,0,,What should we do? Where else might she be?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.84,0:18:54.02,clover,,0,0,0,,Well, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.02,0:18:57.04,clover,,0,0,0,,She's probably with Morita.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.86,0:19:10.27,clover,,0,0,0,,Sensei... this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.90,0:19:18.40,clover,,0,0,0,,Don't tell Hagu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:21.73,clover,,0,0,0,,I want her to make her choice without knowing about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.76,0:19:25.91,clover,,0,0,0,,Are you going to quit Hamabi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.82,0:19:29.71,clover,,0,0,0,,I've decided to take a sabbatical.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.14,0:19:32.69,clover,,0,0,0,,At this rate, I'd be doing a poor job balancing both things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.36,0:19:35.72,clover,,0,0,0,,I'd be inconveniencing the school as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.41,0:19:41.98,clover,,0,0,0,,I thought that I'd dedicate all of the next three years to Hagu's rehab.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.54,0:19:47.44,clover,,0,0,0,,But... to think that her prince would come back at a time like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.15,0:19:51.42,clover,,0,0,0,,Sensei, what if Hagu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.03,0:19:55.89,clover,,0,0,0,,What if she chooses Morita?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.94,0:19:58.42,clover,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.03,0:20:00.32,clover,,0,0,0,,I'll travel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.12,0:20:03.62,clover,,0,0,0,,I'll travel around the world, maybe even twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.09,0:20:05.41,clover,,0,0,0,,It'll be a good opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.41,0:20:08.12,clover,,0,0,0,,I'll travel around the world until I've had enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.74,0:20:12.29,clover,,0,0,0,,Sensei... why won't you tell Hagu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.18,0:20:15.72,clover,,0,0,0,,To Hagu? Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.35,0:20:18.13,clover,,0,0,0,,"Choose me."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.42,0:20:21.95,clover,,0,0,0,,I can't say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.95,0:20:22.97,clover,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.97,0:20:26.59,clover,,0,0,0,,Even though you can abandon everything like this for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.02,0:20:29.50,clover,,0,0,0,,I said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.86,0:20:31.81,clover,,0,0,0,,Even though I didn't even have a sliver of hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.58,0:20:35.04,clover,,0,0,0,,Even though I knew that it was hopeless...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.04,0:20:36.44,clover,,0,0,0,,I still said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.11,0:20:49.15,clover,,0,0,0,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.57,0:20:53.79,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm going back to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.23,0:20:56.28,clover,,0,0,0,,Hagu might have come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.72,0:21:29.86,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}arifurete iru kimochi nante sa
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.72,0:21:29.86,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}It would be so much easier...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.22,0:21:40.32,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}nanimo iwazu ni isso kieteshimaeba
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.22,0:21:40.32,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}...if these stale emotions...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.32,0:21:43.74,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,raku ni nareru no ni
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.32,0:21:43.74,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,...could just disappear without a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.74,0:21:52.87,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}sorezore no michi wo yuku sono wakaremichi
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.74,0:21:52.87,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}At the crossroads where we split ways...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.42,0:22:06.35,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}mou nidoto au koto no nai deai wa kanashisugiru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.42,0:22:06.35,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}...it saddens me to think we may never meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.35,0:22:09.09,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,tarinai kimochi wo mochiyotte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.35,0:22:09.09,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,Despite adding the emotions that are lacking...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.09,0:22:11.95,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,atatameta saki kara hieteitte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.09,0:22:11.95,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,...things cool off just as soon as I warm them...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.95,0:22:16.29,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}sonna hazu naitte shinjiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.95,0:22:16.29,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}...but I still don't want to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.66,0:22:24.99,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}ittai itsumade onaji kotoba wo kakaekondenda
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.66,0:22:24.99,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}Just how long am I going to brood over the same word?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.99,0:22:28.39,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}kakekondenda
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.99,0:22:28.39,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}How long...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.59,0:22:34.75,clover,,0,0,0,,Next episode: Please give me your life.
